Page 1: The Executive Mandate

Purpose: Cognitive Decoupling

ST-T1024 V2.0 marks the end of cloud-dependent AI. It replaces high-entropy, stochastic “black boxes” with a Deterministic Triage-to-Tile Pipeline. This enables sovereign, local execution on standard and embedded hardware with minimal thermal impact and no data leakage.
The 8-to-1 Bit Evolution (The Smooth Passage)
8-Bit Anchor (S8F): Baseline for determinism by eliminating floating-point math and locking logic to physical constants.
1.58-bit Ternary Transition: Moves to 1.58-bit Ternary Logic {-1, 0, 1}. Shifts from arithmetic multiplication to topological matching/flow. Eliminates 8-bit multipliers, shrinking silicon footprint by ~90% and enabling N independent tiles within a smartphone Secure Enclave.

